{"tid":525190,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"6k-7k list 求評","createTime":"2018-01-10T11:25:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-11T22:05:35.000Z","uid":64378,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c759e2dfa2495861180884d4442f6d6384fc9cc3","tid":525190,"uid":64378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T11:25:48.000Z","msg":"是咁的，電腦壞左要換機<br />\n<br />\nBudget大約6k～7k<br />\n<br />\n主要用黎打機(Wow, lol, pubg) 唔洗剪片繪圖, 唔超頻，玩game 唔洗開最高最緊要順<br />\n<br />\n目標係黎緊五年玩到新Game既最低配置（我唔知呢個budget會唔會做到但盡量啦￼ )<br />\n<br />\n上網research 完一輪自己鳩砌左個list<br />\nCPU: Amd ryzen r5 1600 $1555<br />\n<br />\n老母板： Gigabyte GA-AB350 gaming 3 $910<br />\n<br />\nRAM: Kingston value ram series 8gb ddr4 2400mhz c17 $730<br />\n<br />\nDisplay卡： Gigabyte GeForce Gtx1060 G1 Gaming 6gb DDR 5 $2499 Gigabyte GeForce GTX1050Ti D5 4GB ddr 5 $1300<br />\n<br />\nSsd: Samsung PM961 Polaris M.2 PCIE NVMe 3.0 x4 $790<br />\n<br />\n火牛： Acbel ipower m85 series m85 550w semi modular $530<br />\n<br />\n機箱：未諗￼ 想買個火牛係機頂同埋有隔塵網個d , 上網睇唔多覺有，打算去買個陣睇下咩價錢，愈cheap愈好￼ 我唔知價鳩當佢三舊先 $300<br />\n<br />\n風扇加其他零件雜物：$200<br />\n<br />\nHd 用翻舊機個1tb hd<br />\nMon 都係用翻舊<br />\n<br />\nTotal $6315<br />\n<br />\nP.s. ssd 火牛 都係係悠二度搬過黎，我google左一大輪都唔知邊個比較好<br />\n<br />\nP.s.2. 我上網搵psu calculator 計過個power好似爆好多，我諗住留d位將來加野，唔知會唔會預太多￼ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPs 3 faroll 有無伏￼ 上面d價抄faroll ,出去買好似會貴d？ 同埋黃金地下最大個間匯訊（好似係）有無伏，上幾次見佢大間係個度睇住<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n謝謝各巴打￼ ￼ ￼ ￼ ￼ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd1a1c4d73e2770169b9b0eeb08c89e23d4aa502","tid":525190,"uid":21392,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T11:29:03.000Z",